<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GO_0010468> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "This class covers any process that regulates the rate of production of a mature gene product, and so includes processes that regulate that rate by regulating the level, stability or availability of intermediates in the process of gene expression. For example, it covers any process that regulates the level, stability or availability of mRNA or circRNA for translation and thereby regulates the rate of production of the encoded protein via translation." .
