<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_0011821> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> "Connective tissue, which consists of a population of connective tissue cells, the intercellular matrix of which contains an irregular network of collagen and elastic fiber bundles. Examples: areolar tissue, mucoid tissue, connective tissue of peritoneum, connective tissue of fibrous pericardium." .
